title: NFT PROFITS TO BUY BACK YMEN
body: I propose the profits from the NFT's go towards buying Ymen in a marketing wallet which would be used for marketing purposes like for youtube shoutouts, telegram shoutouts, anything marketing related that will bring attention to the project. OR we can use profits to burn Ymen or Mutants.
choices: use nft profits to burn more Ymen
use nft profits to burn Mutants
author: 0xF85acE4D7726c0Cbed293B1122Bc977A101cB90c
